text.tspan: This is one piece of a Split Bitcoin Key. It is given to
the above named trustee to keep safe (i.e. protected
from weather and damage), secret (i.e. it should be
accessed/seen only by the trustee) and secure (i.e.
access by any person other than the owner or trustee
This SBK Piece should be returned only to the owner
upon their request, or upon the death of the owner,
to the executor of their last will.
- you are not the above named trustee,
- this SBK Piece is accessed/seen by any
person other than you as the trustee,
- there is any possibility that a copy or
picture of this SBK Piece was made.
